      • evaluateModelBatchWindow

        public static Result evaluateModelBatchWindow​(MultiLabelClassifier h,
                                              weka.core.Instances D,
                                              int numWindows,
                                              double rLabeled,
                                              String Top,
                                              String Vop)
                                       throws Exception
        EvaluateModelBatchWindow - Evaluate a multi-label data-stream model over windows.
        Parameters:
        h - Multilabel Classifier
        D - stream
        numWindows - number of windows
        rLabeled - labelled-ness (1.0 by default)
        Top - threshold option
        Vop - verbosity option
        Returns:
        The Result on the final window (but it contains samples of all the other evaluated windows). The window is sampled every N/numWindows instances, for a total of numWindows windows.
        Throws:
        Exception

      • evaluateModelPrequentialBasic

        public static Result evaluateModelPrequentialBasic​(MultiXClassifier h,
                                                   weka.core.Instances D,

                                                   String Top,
                                                   String Vop)
                                            throws Exception
        Prequential Evaluation - Accuracy since the start of evaluation.
        Parameters:
        h - Multilabel Classifier
        D - stream
        windowSize - sampling frequency (of evaluation statistics)
        rLabeled - labelled-ness (1.0 by default)
        Top - threshold option
        Vop - verbosity option The window is sampled every N/numWindows instances, for a total of numWindows windows.
        Throws:
        Exception
